rComments: Absolutely horrid. It's so hard to listen to him, he has a tough accent and says "uhh" more than he says anything else. His tests are hard. His exam was brutal. The course is not stimulating whatsoever, very dry material. Never again will I take a course with this professor, ever.

This course is one of the best in the department. Love it and I am thinking of a career in biotechnology sector because of this course. He has an Asian accent, but was never a problem to understand well, just pay attention in class. Definitely recommend.
the course was actually quite fun, a lot of stuff though. overall, a very good instructor.
A great prof. always available to help!
Great prof. Always available for help!

very helpful prof. the course is very stimulating. learned a lot of interesting stuff from the course. Though not a native English speaker, he is easy to follow. Pay attention in classes, you will enjoy!

This is not a very good professor especially since he is hard to follow. Overall he is really confusing and his tests aren't bad but exam was EXTREMELY difficult..wouldn't recommend this course
